description:
Simple vest design. Made from hardened leather.
Effective against fire.
name: Leather vest

description:
A torturers' loincloth with strappings.
Shows a lot skin and muscle.
name: Loincloth

description:
A dark robe used by dark priests. It's rather
minimalistic in design. Offers some warmth.
name: Priest's robe

description:
Upper body armor made with hardened leather.
Great protection against fire.
name: Hard leather armor

description:
Made from pale skins. Use to hide your scent from
ghouls and creatures alike.
name: Ghoul outfit

description:
Made from guard skins. Use to hide your scent from
guards.
name: Guard outfit

description: A hood made of stitched together cloth pieces.
name: Cloth hood

description:
A helmet made of leather. It doesn't fit well, it's
too loose.
name: Leather helmet

description: A simple cape to keep you warm.
name: Cloth cape

description:
An eastern style talisman with decorations depicting
an eclipse of the sun.
name: Eclipse talisman

description:
A crude crown sculpted from stone. The style of the crown
suggests primitive culture.
name: Stone crown

description:
An armor made of leather and wolf pelts. Offers warmth,
but is weak against fire.
name: Fur armor

description:
A dark robe used by higher dark priests. It's rather
minimalistic in design.
name: High priest's robe

description:
A plate mail armor offers great defence, but is rather
clunky to use.
name: Plate mail

description: Very simple black piece.
name: Black dress

description: A simple make-shift shield. It's better than nothing.
name: Wooden buckler

description:
An iron shield with an insignia of a black spider. The
shield is light to use an offers good protection.
name: Spider shield

description:
A shield typically used by the Knights of the Midnight
Sun. The shield has an insignia of an eagle and a sword.
name: Eagle crest shield

description:
A doll found from the cells. It's depicting a long light
brown haired man. The doll gives you eerie vibes.
name: Peculiar doll

description:
An ever watching eye is taking care of you. It seems to
relieve your feelings of fear and terror...
name: Everwatching talisman

description: A pair of arm guard to prevent serious injuries.
name: Arm guards

description: A pair of leg guards to prevent serious injuries.
name: Leg guards

description:
Chainmail hood gives it's users great protection, however
it's a little uncomformtable.
name: Chainmail hood

description:
A heavy helmet that not only gives great protection,
but also prevents confusion and getting stunned.
name: Plate helmet

description:
A plated iron cuirass armour that offers moderate defence.
Without pauldrons it offers good mobility.
name: Iron cuirass

description:
A freshly cut cavewolf paw. It is said to bring good luck,
but surely that's just some nonsense folklore?
name: Cavewolf paw

description:
A magical ring worn once by the great Bethel. The ring
restores mind during encounters.
name: Sorcerer's stone

description:
A cursed ring that is said to make blood still and thus
prevent bleeding. There's no way to explain this but magic.
name: Ring of the still-blood

description:
A ring with a blood diamond embeded on it. The blood diamond
has seen so much death that life force is leaking from it.
name: Ring of wraiths

description:
A cursed ring with thorns that emit steady flow of poison.
Steady flow makes you immune to bigger amounts.
name: Thorned ring

description:
An iron helmet that protect the entire face, including
eyes.
name: Iron mask

description:
A mascot of good luck and fortune. The fact that you can
craft it yourself works as powerful symbolism.
name: Pinecone pig

description:
A plated armor which offers great protection. The armor
has a family insignia of a bird.
name: Gaunt plate armor

description:
A steel military helmet with a face guard. Offers
protection for throat, neck and rest of the head.
name: Gaunt bascinet

description:
The condensed wrath of the Crow Mauler. Increases the 
strength of whoever holds it.
name: Crow Mauler soul

description:
The soul of the Iron Shakespeare enhances the defence
of whoever holds it.
name: Iron shakespeare soul

description:
The soul of the Salmonsnake gives its owner a hardened
skin that prevents limb losses and bleeding.
name: Salmonsnake soul

description:
The soul of the White angel gives its owner swift
movements and an extra turn.
name: White angel soul

description:
The soul of the Black witch gives its owner occult
powers that poison the opponent.
name: Black witch soul

description:
The soul of the Cavemother gives its owner increased
aggression.
name: Cavemother soul

description:
The soul of the Butterfly makes it easier to evade incoming
attacks with a feather light steps.
name: Butterfly soul

description:
The soul of the Old guardian. Just a glimpse of the
determination the guardian had. Prevents you from dying.
name: Old guardian soul

description:
A tattered piece of the red scarf the Old guardian used.
This scarf proves you defeated Old guardian.
name: Red scarf

description:
A heavy trench coat that is made from hardened leather.
Great protection against fire attacks.
name: Trench coat

description:
A silver necklace with a soul stone embedded on it. The
stone protects against otherwordly powers.
name: Soul devour necklace

description:
Made from skinned fur. Use to hide your scent from
furry creatures and beasts alike.
name: Fur outfit

description:
A simple lens worn on one eye. Slightly improves the
accuracy of its wearer.
name: Monocle

description:
You can see the world clearer with these. Improves the
accuracy of its wearer greatly.
name: Eyeglasses

description:
A bottle that contains eastern perfume. The aroma
attracts monsters and beasts of all kind.
name: Eastern perfume

description:
An ancient relic that is said to bind your soul to your
body in all situations.
name: Spirit anchor

description:
A special armor created for the Penance Knights of Vatican.
Once you put the armor on, you cannot remove it anymore.
name: Penance armor

description:
A special armor created for the Penance Knights of Vatican.
Once you put the armor on, you cannot remove it anymore.
name: Penance armor

description:
Silk robes from the far East. Despite looking rather flimsy,
they provide decent protection against otherwordly powers.
name: Eastern silk robes

description:
A stylized and specifically hardened farmer's hat typically used
in the far East. It has been tweaked to be used in a battle.
name: Jingasa kabuto

description:
A charm said to have fallen from the robes of the wandering
warrior Yggaegetsu. Raises critical hit rate of whoever holds it.
name: Charm of the Yggaegetsu

description:
Protects against hand infection and zoophobia.
Convenient and reliable.
name: Hunter's clothing

description:
Provides a strong chance to dodge, 
but the fire becomes much more dangerous for the wearer.
name: Wendigo beast soul

description:
Scary Wendigo Mask.
Can protect the wearer from blindness.
name: Wendigo mask

description:
Increases the wearer's life force, cannot be unequipped.
While also improving their defensive stance.
name: Lizardman berserk soul

description: A strange dog mask taken from the corpse of a lizard.
name: Moonless mask

description:
A shiny horseshoe increases the luck of its wearer.
Contains hidden effects.
name: Horseshoe

description:
A funny talisman of Sylvian, 
increases the healing abilities of the wearer.
name: Talisman Sylvian

description:
Drains the life force from your enemies, 
healing the wearer.
name: Ring of Nosferatu

description:
Ancient knowledge is transmitted to the carrier, 
increasing his mental abilities.
name: Guardian of nature soul

description:
Soul of a powerful witch.
Improves the owner's magical knowledge.
name: High witch soul

description:
The soul of an ancient Nosferatu helps 
the owner restore his vitality during battle.
name: Nosferatu soul

description:
Made with lizard skin.
It's very rough.
name: Lizardman outfit

description:
Elegant vampire lord clothes.
Displayed on each character.
name: Vampire outfit

description:
Wendigo clothing.
If you wear the full set, you will get a disguise
name: Wendigo's clothing

description:
Made with golem flesh
It's very rough and it smells disgusting.
name: Meat boy outfit

description:
A bottle of black essence, you don't understand 
why the contents don't want to leave the bottle...
name: Bottle of black essence

description:
Additional attack to its wearer, your attacks is bleeding.
The talisman merges with your heart and weapon
name: Talisman Gro-Goroth

description:
Beads in the shape of Gro-Goroth's eyes.
Looks crazy, improves critical damage.
name: Eyes of Gro-Goroth

description:
A golden cuirass armour that offers good defence. 
Without pauldrons it offers good mobility.
name: Golden cuirass

description:
An Pocketcat mask that protect the entire face, including
eyes.
name: Pocketcat mask

description:
According to legend, the tooth belongs to some 
forgotten god and endows the bearer with darkness.
name: God of depth tooth

description:
A sprout born from a Vinushka is a part of our nature.
Enhances Vinushka's magic and more...
name: Child of Vinushka

description:
Cross symbolizing the crucifixion of Alllmer.
Protects the wearer from the otherworld.
name: Alllmer's Cross

description:
Cave dweller camouflage.
Looks weird.
name: Cavedweller outfit

description:
Armor of a high-ranking knight.
Protects the limbs well, as well as the face.
name: Glorious Knight's Armor

description:
Armor of a knight.
Protects the limbs well, as well as the face.
name: Knight's Armor

description:
Soul of the purest darkness.
Enhances the darkness within the wearer.
name: Darkness soul

description:
This doesn't even look like clothing.
Are you trying to appeal to pity by wearing this clothing?
name: Beggar's clothes

description:
A very beautiful teddy bear, girls love toys like this.
Increases the owner's self-confidence.
name: Cute bear toy

description:
A very strong and large shield.
Protects the wearer from being stunned.
name: Praetorian Shield
